</head>
<body class="secondary-page">
<div class="page">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="main">
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Contact Us</h1>
                <p>Reach out to us at <a href="tel:+19414020472">+1 (941) 402-0472</a> or send a message using the form below. We aim to respond to all legitimate inquiries within 24 hours.</p>

                <form action="/submit-contact-form" method="post" class="contact-form">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="first-name">First Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="first-name" name="first-name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="last-name">Last Name</label>
                            <input type="text" id="last-name" name="last-name" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message">Your Message</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Send Message</button>
                </form>

                <div class="contact-info">
                    <h3>Our Office</h3>
                    <p>EmpState Web</p>
                    <p>1234 Web Lane</p>
                    <p>New York, NY 10001</p>
                </div>

                <div class="customer-service">
                    <h3>Your Dedicated Customer Service Representative</h3>
                    <p>As a New York-based web design company, we pride ourselves on providing personalized service. You'll always have a direct line to a real person. For any questions, feel free to reach out to Ilia Oborin directly at <a href="tel:+19414020472">+1 (941) 402-0472</a> or use the contact form above. All submissions go directly to Ilia's inbox.</p>
                    <p>We are committed to ensuring you feel confident in choosing us for your web design needs. Our business thrives on referrals and repeat customers, and we look forward to serving you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</div>
<script src="assets/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
